OL,3,CAlmost 30 litigations launched in
OL,4,Cconnection with cervical screening
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FAlmost 30 women have taken legal
OL,8,Faction against Northern Ireland's five
OL,9,Fhealth trusts since 2013 over the
OL,10,Faccuracy of their cervical smears, UTV
OL,11,Fcan reveal.
OL,13,FThese litigations were launched even
OL,14,Fbefore the Southern Health Trust was
OL,15,Fforced to review 17,500 women's
OL,16,Fresults last year.
OL,18,FIt comes as campaigners prepare to
OL,19,Ftake their fight for a statutory
OL,20,Fpublic inquiry to Westminster.
