OL,7,FSandra and Ron Courtney spoke to UTV
OL,8,Fon Thursday as part of a special
OL,9,Finvestigation into the cervical cancer
OL,10,Fscreening scandal.
OL,12,FTheir daughter Lynsey, died after her
OL,13,Ffirst ever smear test was misread.
OL,15,FThey told UTV about their six-year
OL,16,Fbattle to get answers from the
OL,17,FSouthern Health Trust about what went
OL,18,Fwrong.
