OL,7,F"We don't want to have to go through
OL,8,Fwhat we went through when it could be
OL,9,Fprevented.
OL,11,F"You know, families shouldn't have to
OL,12,Fgo through that sort of trauma", they
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FSadly, Lynsey was not the only woman
OL,16,Ffailed by years of mistakes within the
OL,17,FSouthern Health Trusts screening lab.
