OL,7,FErin Harbinson died last month
OL,8,Ffollowing three misread smears, and
OL,9,Fother women have had to be treated for
OL,10,Fcancer that was preventable.
OL,12,FA major investigation by UTV revealed
OL,13,Fsignificant shortcomings stretching
OL,14,Fback as far as 2008 that were left
OL,15,Flargely unaddressed.
OL,17,FShortcomings that the Courtney family
OL,18,Ftried to draw attention to but nothing
OL,19,Fwas done.
