OL,7,FUTV's findings have been met with
OL,8,Fanger by campaigners who want a
OL,9,Fstatutory public inquiry into the
OL,10,Fscandal.
OL,12,FHeather Thompson from the group Ladies
OL,13,Fwith Letters said: "I am angry.
OL,14,FDisgusted, probably is a better term
OL,15,Ffor me to use.
OL,17,F"I think it is dreadful that this was
OL,18,Fallowed to run on for such a long time
OL,19,Fand that's why I feel that it is so
OL,20,Fimportant.
