OL,7,F"We have spoken to the Health
OL,8,FMinister. We are really hoping that he
OL,9,Fwill, whenever he has all the data
OL,10,Fback and all the information from the
OL,11,FSouthern Trust at the end of the
OL,12,Freview, that he will consider
OL,13,Fdefinitely initiating a statutory
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry.
